<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-5">

      <div class="col-lg-7 about-fade">
        <span class="about-section-label">About Get Kinder</span>
        <h1 class="about-hero__headline">
          What if kindness<br>was <em>contagious?</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero__sub">
          We're a registered nonprofit using technology as a force for good —
          connecting volunteers, organizations, and donors in one transparent loop
          that makes showing up easier, and showing it counts.
        </p>
        <a href="/events" class="about-hero__cta">Find an opportunity near you →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-5 text-center about-fade" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
        <img src="./images/heart3D.png" alt="Get Kinder Heart" class="about-hero__visual" style="width:200px;">
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ STORY ══ -->
<section class="about-story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row g-5 align-items-start">

      <div class="col-lg-5 about-fade">
        <span class="about-section-label">Our Story</span>
        <p class="about-story__pull">
          Built by people who lived<br>the <em>broken system</em><br>firsthand.
        </p>
        <p class="about-story__attribution">Vancouver, BC · Est. 2024</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-7 about-story__body about-fade" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        <p>
          <strong>Get Kinder started with a frustration.</strong> Our founders spent years on
          both sides of the community table — running organizations that struggled to find
          reliable volunteers, donating money into black holes with no proof of impact, and
          watching talented, willing people give up because the process was too hard.
        </p>
        <p>
          The tools didn't exist. Organizations coordinated in spreadsheets. Volunteers had
          no record of what they'd contributed. Donors had no idea where their money went.
          The system was broken — and everyone inside it knew it.
        </p>
        <p>
          So we built the infrastructure that should have existed all along: a verified impact
          loop where every shift is recorded, every dollar is traced, and every act of kindness
          leaves a real mark on a real community.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Kinder AI™</strong> — trademarked in Canada — makes it effortless.
          Not just good intentions. <em>Verified impact.</em>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ BELIEF STRIP ══ -->
<div class="about-belief">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="about-belief__text about-fade">
      "Doing good <em>feels good.</em> We just make it easier to do —
      and impossible to ignore when you do."
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══ PILLARS ══ -->
<section class="about-pillars">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="text-center mb-5 about-fade">
      <span class="about-section-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)">What We Stand For</span>
      <h2 class="about-pillars__headline">Purpose. Mission. Vision.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">

      <div class="col-lg-4 about-fade">
        <div class="about-pillar">
          <img class="about-pillar__icon" src="./images/heart-in-hands-3D.png" alt="">
          <p class="about-pillar__label">Purpose</p>
          <h3 class="about-pillar__title">Our Story</h3>
          <p class="about-pillar__body">
            Inspired by the simple question: <em>What if kindness was contagious?</em>
            We use Kinder AI™ and innovative AI for Good strategies to make it easy to
            start kindness habits — and share, celebrate, and inspire kindness in others.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 about-fade" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="about-pillar">
          <img class="about-pillar__icon" src="./images/chatheart-3D.png" alt="">
          <p class="about-pillar__label">Mission</p>
          <h3 class="about-pillar__title">Make Kindness Effortless</h3>
          <p class="about-pillar__body">
            Transforming individual actions into global change — making the world kinder
            and happier. Kinder AI™ supports daily kindness habits that improve well-being,
            build community, and align with the
            <a href="https://sdgs.un.org/goals" target="_blank">UN's 17 SDGs</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 about-fade" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="about-pillar">
          <img class="about-pillar__icon" src="./images/heart-megaphone-3d.png" alt="">
          <p class="about-pillar__label">Vision</p>
          <h3 class="about-pillar__title">A Kinder World</h3>
          <p class="about-pillar__body">
            As part of the <a href="https://getkindr.com/" target="_blank">Get Kindr Foundation</a>,
            we envision a kinder, more compassionate world driven by AI for Good — fostering
            resilience, strengthening communities, and amplifying global happiness, one
            intentional act at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ TEAM ══ -->
<section class="about-team">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="mb-5 about-fade">
      <span class="about-section-label">The Founders</span>
      <h2 class="about-team__headline">
        People who chose to<br><em>do something about it.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">

      <div class="col-lg-4 about-fade">
        <div class="about-founder">
          <div class="about-founder__photo-wrap">
            <img src="./images/erin.png" alt="Erin Gray">
          </div>
          <div class="about-founder__body">
            <p class="about-founder__role">Co-Founder & CEO</p>
            <h3 class="about-founder__name">Erin Gray</h3>
            <blockquote class="about-founder__quote">
              "I've closed deals worth millions. The most meaningful thing I've ever done is show up for my community."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="about-founder__bio">
              Shaped by a family culture of volunteering, Erin earned her master's in London and went on to
              build commercial relationships across Dubai and the Middle East. She brings that global expertise
              back to what matters most — infrastructure that actually works for people running our communities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 about-fade" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="about-founder">
          <div class="about-founder__photo-wrap">
            <img src="./images/michael.png" alt="Michael Wozney">
          </div>
          <div class="about-founder__body">
            <p class="about-founder__role">Co-Founder & COO</p>
            <h3 class="about-founder__name">Michael Wozney</h3>
            <blockquote class="about-founder__quote">
              "Kindness isn't soft — it's the most effective leadership strategy I've ever seen."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="about-founder__bio">
              A psychology degree and years running a community services organization gave Michael a
              ground-floor view of what broken infrastructure costs volunteers and communities. An MBA
              and 15+ years coaching leaders in healthcare and global multinationals taught him how to
              scale culture. Now he's doing both at once.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 about-fade" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="about-founder">
          <div class="about-founder__photo-wrap">
            <img src="./images/tate.png" alt="Tate Wozney">
          </div>
          <div class="about-founder__body">
            <p class="about-founder__role">Co-Founder</p>
            <h3 class="about-founder__name">Tate Wozney</h3>
            <blockquote class="about-founder__quote">
              "If it doesn't feel natural to someone my age, we haven't finished building it."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="about-founder__bio">
              The youngest — and the most important voice in the room for a platform built to resonate with
              the next generation. Tate brings genuine passion for volunteering and the critically honest
              perspective of someone who will actually live in the world Get Kinder is trying to build.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ CLOSING CTA ══ -->
<section class="about-closing">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="about-closing__eyebrow">Ready to do something real?</p>
    <h2 class="about-closing__headline">
      The world gets kinder<br>when <em>you</em> do.
    </h2>
    <p class="about-closing__sub">
      Join the loop. Volunteer your time, fund verified impact,
      or bring your organization onto the platform — for free.
    </p>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
      <a href="/events" class="about-btn-primary">🙋 Start volunteering →</a>
      <a href="/donate" class="about-btn-secondary">💚 Fund verified impact →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="about-closing__caption">
      Verified attendance. Transparent funding. Real community outcomes.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
